  <brief_title>Proper Dosage of Ketamine in Intravenous Regional Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Proper Dosage of Intravenous Ketamine When Used as an Adjuvant to Lidocaine in Intravenous Regional Anesthesia (IVRA).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University Health Network, Toronto</agency>
